{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Kizuyami</strong> is a first-person atmospheric psychological horror game that is set in Japan in the 1990s. Will you be able to uncover the mysteries and find your way out? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WASD - Movement/Swap Item (While Inventory is active)<br>Left Shift (Hold) - Inventory<br>Left-Click - Interact/Use Equipped Item<br>ESC - Pause Menu</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Enter The Unknown</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You find yourself in a never-ending Japanese street where no matter which direction you go, you cannot leave. You stumble upon the same house over and over again, which calls for you in inexplicable ways. Answer the call.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602820/extras/Street.gif?t=1730472068\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Investigate Strange Houses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every house has it's dark, shrouded story embbeded inside. Even though it seems usual at first glance, you can feel something is off. Uncover the mystery. Try to make sense of the unknown. Survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602820/extras/The_House.gif?t=1730472068\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features &amp; Extras</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 houses to explore and investigate the story behind. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with various objects, make a path through everything that is in your way to get out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survive the unknown.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2602820/extras/Kizuyami.gif?t=1730472068\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2602820?t=1730472